{"tid":1996140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［天馬］行動建議-普通衫、試水溫","createTime":"2020-04-30T18:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T03:42:03.000Z","uid":145847,"like":5,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"253daa86ff564f846f3ac884fd83a5fa23d969eb","tid":1996140,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"成個抗爭暫停左幾個月<br />\n唔係咁快恢復到熱度<br />\n陣間未必會好多人<br />\n所以陣間最主要係試吓水溫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議大家盡量唔好blackbloc, <br />\n普通衫到場即可<br />\n帶多兩件唔同顏色衫換<br />\n除左掉嘢出路唔好做其他野<br />\n走果陣兜遠路返屋企，做反跟蹤eg.坐地鐵臨閂門果下突然衝出去已經得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁樣係小人既狀況下，反而更加難target特定人<br />\n就算捉到你都只係衰公眾㤃擾/違反限聚令/非法集結，非常細罪，後果非常細"},{"pid":"1cdbbc8f75203982ba8ec14994c51922a4645ad3","tid":1996140,"uid":1767,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"你咁講完已經Confirm天馬行動係咩人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc941241ff5278650ab064390c9296b25d0efe2","tid":1996140,"uid":178364,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">就算捉到你都只係衰公眾㤃擾/違反限聚令/非法集結，非常細罪，後果非常細</code></pre><br />\n好撚鬼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d987167098adae951fde7bbbc752b08df7c4b1f","tid":1996140,"uid":22624,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"天馬行動一定係引手足，大家做下街坊好喇"},{"pid":"e63e84c593bd2eb1e1602c25e9cb409a6a82b925","tid":1996140,"uid":13176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:55:21.000Z","msg":"[天馬] 預左比人屌 聽日天馬唔好出啦 伏呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n五一黃金週同所謂天馬行動根本有衝突。前排紅媒不斷妖魔化黃色經濟圈，封路既話大家都幫襯唔到黃店，邊個最開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060e8d1d4e8b84208479fe6455ab1857061142ae","tid":1996140,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">輕裝好,唔好帶gear,因為只係試下水溫</span></span><br />\n見到狗,冷靜,扮路人向後走<br />\n你著普通街衫,佢好難識別邊個係target<br />\n自己執生"},{"pid":"b06e3770b04e4a6bed6a72b96612a3727f5d3fa2","tid":1996140,"uid":145847,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6d987167098adae951fde7bbbc752b08df7c4b1f","tid":1996140,"uid":22624,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"天馬行動一定係引手足，大家做下街坊好喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"做街坊好,做緊要夠人多,人多先比到機會行動既手足融入人群走到,同埋狗都難target 特定人"},{"pid":"109755d8fd9d2b194284b990a12dad8ab803373d","tid":1996140,"uid":145847,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"cfc941241ff5278650ab064390c9296b25d0efe2","tid":1996140,"uid":178364,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:49:08.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">就算捉到你都只係衰公眾㤃擾/違反限聚令/非法集結，非常細罪，後果非常細</code></pre><br />\n好撚鬼啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:03:39.000Z","msg":"我唔係讀law,可能講錯<br />\n限聚令只係罰2000,<br />\n非法集結黃之鋒案為例,黃之鋒,羅冠聰被判社會服務令120小時；黃之鋒及周永康被判80小時,只係做義工<br />\n公眾㤃擾我就唔知,好少引用"},{"pid":"d9f769a1d8fb1ce052157dca3cc140d9a98c0345","tid":1996140,"uid":167928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量唔好blackbloc 除左掉嘢出路唔好做其他野</span><br />\nCCTV已經認得你參與暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71aab66d6193ada474dd7e7377047f069d9de5e","tid":1996140,"uid":145847,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"d9f769a1d8fb1ce052157dca3cc140d9a98c0345","tid":1996140,"uid":167928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:07:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量唔好blackbloc 除左掉嘢出路唔好做其他野</span><br />\nCCTV已經認得你參與暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma